      <title>戴尔推出类似苹果的品牌重塑，力图让 PC 再次酷起来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/dell-rebrand-of-pcs-echoes-apple-naming-conventions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了刺激需求，戴尔科技公司 (Dell Technologies Inc.) 正在对其个人电脑进行重新品牌重塑，其命名方式让人联想到苹果公司的命名惯例。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/dell-rebrand-of-pcs-echoes-apple-naming-conventions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 19:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AMD 首次将戴尔列为商用 PC 客户</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/amd-adds-dell-as-commercial-pc-customer-for-the-first-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球第二大计算机处理器制造商超微半导体公司 (Advanced Micro Devices Inc.) 表示，其芯片将首次被戴尔科技公司用于销售给企业的个人电脑中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/amd-adds-dell-as-commercial-pc-customer-for-the-first-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 19:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>LG 电子与微软合作打造家庭人工智能</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/lg-electronics-partners-with-microsoft-to-build-ai-for-homes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[LG 电子公司正在与微软公司合作，在其消费电子产品中使用这家美国软件制造商的人工智能技术。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/lg-electronics-partners-with-microsoft-to-build-ai-for-homes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 18:09:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将腾讯列入中国军方黑名单后，腾讯股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/us-adds-tencent-to-chinese-military-blacklist-shares-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[腾讯控股有限公司是一家业务遍布全球的社交媒体和游戏公司，该公司股价周一在美国交易中下跌，此前美国国防部称该科技公司是一家在美国运营的中国军工企业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/us-adds-tencent-to-chinese-military-blacklist-shares-decline</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 16:48:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 禁令将苹果、谷歌推入中美地缘政治纷争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/tiktok-ban-thrusts-apple-google-into-us-china-geopolitical-fray</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TikTok 的创作者正在发布视频，宣传如何绕过美国即将关闭的该应用程序，这可能给苹果公司、Alphabet Inc. 的谷歌和其他依法被要求执行禁令的美国科技公司带来麻烦，否则可能面临数十亿美元的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/tiktok-ban-thrusts-apple-google-into-us-china-geopolitical-fray</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 16:37:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谷歌将把 Gemini AI 引入运行其软件的电视机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/google-to-bring-gemini-ai-to-tv-sets-running-its-software-ces</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet Inc. 的消费者团队将通过在其 Google Assistant 语音控制系统中添加 Gemini，为运行其 Google TV 操作系统的电视机提供 AI 升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/google-to-bring-gemini-ai-to-tv-sets-running-its-software-ces</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高通的新芯片将把人工智能带入 600 美元的个人电脑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/qualcomm-s-new-chips-will-bring-ai-to-600-personal-computers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高通公司推出了新型芯片，旨在为运行最新人工智能软件的个人电脑提供动力，但售价仅为 600 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/qualcomm-s-new-chips-will-bring-ai-to-600-personal-computers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MicroStrategy 在增加优先认购权后购买比特币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/microstrategy-buys-bitcoin-after-adding-preferred-stock-offering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MicroStrategy Inc. 宣布将使用永久优先股以及普通股和债务来购买更多加密货币，随后购买了价值 1.01 亿美元的比特币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/microstrategy-buys-bitcoin-after-adding-preferred-stock-offering</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 13:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
